      "date": "2014-07-17 18:23:22.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: Verified-1\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/691a721e-0ddf-11e4-af8b-5254006e85c2).  Ran 2 tests.  1 tests failed: lustre-initialization-1.",
